last night after all this
is kind of ridiculous,

12:18.200 --> 12:20.498
and I'm not sure I'm up
for the other conversation,

12:20.500 --> 12:22.092
so can you just...

12:22.100 --> 12:24.637
Let me keep trying
to ignore both.

12:25.500 --> 12:28.435
We all have
our ways of coping.

12:32.310 --> 12:34.232
But, if you need to talk...

12:36.550 --> 12:39.610
go ahead.
Not if you're
uncomfortable, or...

12:39.620 --> 12:44.512
I'm fine.
It's probably healthier
not to ignore it. So, um...

12:45.220 --> 12:48.018
Do you think
it's starting up again?

12:52.200 --> 12:54.088
Yeah. Yeah, I do.

12:54.100 --> 12:57.092
Why did he do it
