13:16.620 --> 13:18.019
Or the hero.

13:22.430 --> 13:25.092
I'm a huge fan of the morgue.

13:25.460 --> 13:26.620
I love your voice,

13:26.630 --> 13:29.667
and I think that you make...

13:29.670 --> 13:32.389
The morbid beautiful.

13:32.410 --> 13:34.196
Oh, well, thank you.

13:34.210 --> 13:37.008
