your feelings about mortality

13:41.980 --> 13:44.676
and turning your friend's death
into a puzzle you can solve,

13:44.680 --> 13:47.274
without actually
dealing with it.

13:47.290 --> 13:48.439
Ouch.

13:48.450 --> 13:52.750
I'm sorry.
No, no. You're...
you're probably right.

13:53.430 --> 13:55.284
(Sighs)

13:55.290 --> 13:58.396
We all have
our ways of coping.

14:00.000 --> 14:04.266
