14:33.330 --> 14:34.399
I-i need help.

14:34.400 --> 14:36.197
Don't look at me.

14:36.200 --> 14:38.339
Hey, what do you have
in your locker?

14:38.340 --> 14:41.138
Don't worry about it.
I'll be right back.

14:41.140 --> 14:42.664
Oh, I can't believe
he just said that.

14:42.680 --> 14:46.332
Um, okay, yeah, I'll go
with him, keep a lookout.

14:46.350 --> 14:48.409
Are you sure about that?
Yes.

14:48.410 --> 14:50.469
