What? Why?

14:55.590 --> 14:58.218
Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Wait a minute!
My friend is about to vomit.

14:58.220 --> 15:01.519
Can you please take us
to the ladies' room?
No, I can't...

15:01.530 --> 15:04.351
Okay, okay.
Come on, come on. Let's go.

15:06.600 --> 15:08.795
