from the bathroom, deputy.

15:42.800 --> 15:46.531
Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Let me see the bag.

15:46.540 --> 15:48.701
Let me see the bag.

15:50.880 --> 15:52.677
(Mouthing)

16:03.790 --> 16:05.678
So, how do you want
to do this?

16:05.690 --> 16:07.555
Just cuff me, sheriff.

16:07.560 --> 16:09.187
My dad was a cop.
I know how this works.

16:09.190 --> 16:12.296
And you were arrested before.
I do my homework.

16:12.300 --> 16:14.689
So, you know there's
a lot of ways it can play out.

16:14.700 --> 16:16.895
There seems
to be one 0bVIOUS one.

16:16.900 --> 16:17.969
Not really...

16:17.970 --> 16:19.858
Because someone
who goes to the trouble

16:19.870 --> 16:21.701
to stage a big show
like the one that we just saw,

16:21.710 --> 16:26.977
doesn't make the mistake
of leaving a gun
in his locker, right?

16:29.320 --> 16:31.049
It's my dad's gun.
Yeah.

16:31.050 --> 16:32.938
I carry it to protect
myself and my friends.

16:32.950 --> 16:36.738
I suppose that's understandable
after what you've been through.

16:36.760 --> 16:39.752
Thank you
for recognizing that.

16:40.130 --> 16:42.587
I don't blame you
for needing to feel safe.

16:42.600 --> 16:44.056
I'm gonna confiscate
this weapon,

16:44.060 --> 16:49.088
but I'm willing to look past
this entire episode, if...

16:49.100 --> 16:51.295
If...?
If you let me keep
an eye on you.

16:51.300 --> 16:55.236
I think it'd be good for you
to come down to the station.
I may put you to work.

16:55.240 --> 16:57.731
Look, I don't have to tell you.
Cops take care of their own.

16:57.740 --> 17:00.971
Okay? Your dad would've done
the same thing for my kid.

17:02.720 --> 17:04.142
Not my dad.

17:04.150 --> 17:09.884
And don't get me wrong,
i appreciate you
not cuffing me, but...

17:09.890 --> 17:14.623
This whole good cop routine,
it's not playing.

17:14.630 --> 17:17.053
What do you
really want, sheriff?

17:20.130 --> 17:24.226
I want an in, and you're
gonna get me there...

17:24.240 --> 17:27.698
Or you'll be arrested,
put on probation,

17:27.710 --> 17:30.008
and kicked out of school.

17:31.980 --> 17:33.607
Your choice.

17:36.280 --> 17:37.975
(Sighs)

17:40.820 --> 17:43.288
May I offer you
a phone plan?

17:43.290 --> 17:45.281
Okay, if you're trying
to be funny, don't.

17:45.290 --> 17:49.954
I, uh... couldn't help
but overhear. (Chuckles)

17:49.960 --> 17:52.053
