18:02.210 --> 18:03.632
Okay, what's your plan?

18:03.640 --> 18:05.232
Ditch it.
Fast as you can.

18:05.240 --> 18:07.208
Yes. Thank you.
How would I?

18:07.210 --> 18:10.373
Wipe off any prints
and stick it somewhere
they'll find it.

18:10.380 --> 18:12.917
Behind a book
or in the garbage.

18:12.920 --> 18:15.309
Then, it's not connected
to you anymore.

18:15.320 --> 18:18.881
(Phone vibrating)

18:24.730 --> 18:25.992
Hey.
Kieran got busted.

18:26.000 --> 18:29.367
